                          <SHORT-NAME>CddSentHWUnitId</SHORT-NAME>
                          <DESC>
                            <L-2 L="EN">This parameter provides the HW unit ID which is unique in a given CddSent Driver. The value for this parameter starts with 0 and continue without any gaps.</L-2>
